\begin_layout Standard
根据内积的“共轭对称性”，显然有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\langle u\vert v\rangle=(\langle v\vert u\rangle)^{*}\eqqcolon\langle v\vert u\rangle^{*},\quad\langle u\vert\hat{A}\vert v\rangle=\langle u\vert\hat{A}v\rangle=\langle\hat{A}v\vert u\rangle{}^{*}
\]

\end_inset

但一般而言
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\langle u\vert\hat{A}v\rangle=\langle\hat{A}v\vert u\rangle{}^{*}\ne\langle v\vert\hat{A}u\rangle{}^{*}=\langle\hat{A}u\vert v\rangle
\]

\end_inset

为了让 
\begin_inset Formula $\langle u\vert\hat{A}\vert v\rangle$
\end_inset

 对左矢和右矢具有对称性，即使得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\langle\hat{A}u\vert v\rangle=\langle u\vert\hat{A}\vert v\rangle=\langle u\vert\hat{A}v\rangle
\]

\end_inset

需令 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{A}$
\end_inset

 满足某些条件。
